        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "PLASTIC FREE NON TOXIC FOOD STORAGE: Upgrade your kitchen with a healthier alternative to plastic containers; Made from durable clear glass with a food safe silicone lid, these glass storage containers provide non toxic food storage for pantry organization, meal prep, leftovers, and everyday kitchen use",
