                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "MICROWAVE REFRIGERATOR AND DISHWASHER SAFE: Designed for everyday kitchen convenience, these durable glass food containers are safe for microwave reheating (remove lid), dishwasher cleaning and freezer storage; Easily store leftovers, prep meals, or organize pantry items with versatile containers built for modern kitchens",
