        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Use them individually or combine all three sizes to create a coordinated pantry organization system, that keeps your kitchen tidy while maintaining a clean, modern aesthetic. Free from plastic and made with non-toxic materials, the Beille Glass Storage Containers provide a healthier and more sustainable way to store food while elevating the look of your kitchen.<br/><br/>Upgrade kitchen storage with the Beille Ribbed Glass Food Storage Containers, an elegant and practical solution for organizing pantry ingredients, leftovers, snacks and meal prep items. Designed with a modern clear ribbed texture and soft silicone lid, these containers combine modern kitchen style with everyday functionality. Whether used individually or as a coordinated set, they provide a reliable plastic free alternative for safe food storage.<br/><br/>Each container is crafted from durable clear glass that allows you to easily see contents at a glance, while adding a subtle decorative touch to your countertop or pantry shelves. The vertical ribbed design gives the container a refined, modern appearance.<br/><br/>The airtight silicone lid helps lock in freshness and protect ingredients from moisture and air exposure. This secure seal makes the containers ideal for storing dry pantry goods such as coffee beans, pasta, grains, sugar, snacks, nuts and baking ingredients, while also working perfectly for leftovers or prepared foods.<br/><br/>Designed for everyday convenience, these glass containers are microwave, dishwasher, and freezer safe, making them versatile enough for food storage, reheating, and long term ingredient preservation. The lightweight design ensures easy handling while still maintaining the durability and strength expected from high-quality glass kitchenware.<br/><br/>Available in three practical sizes, you can choose the container that best fits your storage needs:<br/><br/>18 oz (550 ml) – Perfect for snacks, spices, herbs and small ingredients<br/><br/>37 oz (1100 ml) – Ideal for grains, cereal, leftovers and meal prep<br/><br/>54 oz (1600 ml) – Great for pasta, baking ingredients or bulk pantry storage<br/><br/>Use them individually or combine all three sizes to create a coordinated pantry organization system, that keeps your kitchen tidy while maintaining a clean, modern aesthetic. Free from plastic and made with non-toxic materials, the Beille Glass Storage Containers provide a healthier and more sustainable way to store food while elevating the look of your kitchen.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
